Package com.symantec.dlpx.flexresponse

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Credential
    A credential suitable for accessing a content repository.
    Plugin
    A FlexResponse plugin.
    PluginMetadata
    The metadata is a way that the plugin may programmatically declare information about itself to the FlexResponse runtime.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ConfiguredPlugin
    When you want to write a plugin that received configuration parameters when it is constructed, you can make use of this class.
    DefaultPluginMetadata
    This class gives you a default implementation of plugin metadata.
